5 Sec. 13. 35-A MRSA §3904, sub-§4, as enacted by PL 1987, c. 141, Pt. A, §6, is
6 amended to read:
7 4. Favorable vote. If, in each municipality, a majority of the legal votes cast on this
8 question favor incorporation, a municipal power district may be created for those
9 municipalities under this chapter upon declaration of the vote of the municipal officers,
10 provided that as long as the total number of votes cast in each municipality for and against
11 the incorporation equals or exceeds 40% 20% of the total votes cast in the municipality for
